{"problem": "In right triangle $ABC$, we have $\angle BAC = 90^\circ$ and $D$ is on $\overline{AC}$ such that $\overline{BD}$ bisects $\angle ABC$. If $AB = 12$ and $BC = 15$, then what is $\cos \angle BDC$?", "level": "Level 5", "type": "Geometry", "solution": "[asy]

